<p><strong>十年马术围栏匠心研发，八年马场建设深耕细作</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/8ca76c1c32a4425ab043c9f8e712a69e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
